item.title: My new photography YouTube channel
item.description: Hello friends! It’s been a while without an update. I’ve been working more and more on my photography endeavors, which includes building up a YouTube channel to document my travels and also my learnings. I’m hoping it’s interesting and useful enough, especially for other aspiring photographers. This year is definitely shaping up to be a year of travelling, and I’d also like to keep a blog of photos and such, so I’m working to get a separate photography blog setup at my photography website.
